{"tid":1903004,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"電訊報：若因新冠縮短英超賽程，無法保證利物浦能奪冠","createTime":"2020-02-28T16:32:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T18:34:03.000Z","uid":173952,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8512258ecad9d9e2b89b22be595a2371e67fc2af","tid":1903004,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T16:32:19.000Z","msg":"2月28日訊 據《每日電訊報》報導，若因新冠病毒影響導致英超縮短賽程，無法保證利物浦能拿到冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n 同樣，聯賽后三名是否還會被降級，也無法得到保證，因為降級關係到數億英鎊的損失。<br />\n<br />\n 因為新冠病毒的傳播，政府可能會取消未來至少2個月的各種體育賽事，這也意味著被叫停的比賽可能永遠不會再次舉行。<br />\n<br />\n 在1939-1940賽季，英格蘭頂級聯賽只進行了三場比賽，就因二戰爆發而被取消，當時的布萊克浦在頂級聯賽中排名第一，領先第二1分。"},{"pid":"5e3d959b243d92e944f5a5bd6ff945b1db89a174","tid":1903004,"uid":186071,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T16:33:33.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 英足總 又逼害我利"},{"pid":"3765fdf0bf09d215ded55030ca755e4e0530ee3e","tid":1903004,"uid":173952,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5e3d959b243d92e944f5a5bd6ff945b1db89a174","tid":1903004,"uid":186071,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T16:33:33.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 英足總 又逼害我利"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T16:45:59.000Z","msg":"武漢錯"},{"pid":"2c1d887296743e779f06fef3eaa5b3398790924d","tid":1903004,"uid":50041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T16:50:24.000Z","msg":"即係點?今屆冠軍空缺?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41535f1b99926a1ea6583fffa1349866e0298d88","tid":1903004,"uid":5649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2c1d887296743e779f06fef3eaa5b3398790924d","tid":1903004,"uid":50041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T16:50:24.000Z","msg":"即係點?今屆冠軍空缺?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T16:51:28.000Z","msg":"民主少少吧，20隊投票決定取唔取消今季排名"},{"pid":"5e10151ebc5cbeacbf456f5d199df379a56e127e","tid":1903004,"uid":43785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2c1d887296